
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link href="/styles/main.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
  integrity="sha384-aFq/bzH65dt+w6FI2ooMVUpc+21e0SRygnTpmBvdBgSdnuTN7QbdgL+OapgHtvPp" crossorigin="anonymous">

</head>

<header class="d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-center py-3 mb-1 border-bottom" id="gradient-background" >
  <a href="/" class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3 mb-md-0 me-md-auto link-body-emphasis text-decoration-none">
    <svg class="bi me-2" width="40" height="32"><use xlink:href="#bootstrap"></use></svg>
    <span class="fs-4" style="color:white">Investmeter</span>
  </a>

  <ul class="nav nav-pills">
    <li class="nav-item"><a href="/" class="nav-link" id="one" style="color:white">Stocks Data</a></li>
    <li class="nav-item"><a href="/news" class="nav-link" id="one" style="color:white">News</a></li>
    <li class="nav-item"><a href="/blog" class="nav-link" id="one" style="color:white">Posts</a></li>
    <li class="nav-item"><a href="/write" class="nav-link" id="one" style="color:white">Contribute</a></li>
  </ul>
</header>

<div class="justify-content-end">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6"></div>
    <div class="text-end col-md-6">
      <% if (locals.loggedin==false) { %>
        
          <form action="/signin" class="m-1">
          <button  class="btn btn-outline-dark" type="submit">Sign In | Sign Up</button>
          </form>
        
          </div>
     
      <% } else if(locals.loggedin==true) {%>
        
        <form action="/signout" class="mt-1">
          <button  class="btn btn-danger " type="submit">Sign Out</button>
        </form>
        <%}%>
    </div>
  </div>
  </div>

<body>
  <% if (locals.content.length===0){ %>
<main class="container">


    <div class="container">
    <h2 style="color: rgb(147, 7, 7); font-size: 15pt; ">
      Wrong stock name, try again
      </h2>
      </div>
    <form action="/news/choose" method="POST">
        
        <div class="container mb-5 ">
          <div class="form-floating " id="firstContainer" >
            <input class="form-control " id="floatingInput" name="stock" type="text"  >
            <label for="floatingInput" >Search for your desired stock news</label> 
            <div >
              <button class="btn btn-dark py-2 btn-lg my-1" type="submit">Search</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>

        <div class="container">
          <h1 style="visibility: hidden;">
            Lorem ipsum odor amet, consectetuer adipiscing elit. Facilisis massa semper pretium purus torquent at mattis nisl erat. Sem elit egestas fringilla eu neque luctus. Posuere est vestibulum felis; euismod suscipit felis. Mi integer justo bibendum lacus, turpis risus rhoncus suscipit. Ultrices elit faucibus metus inceptos, bibendum turpis ultricies. Conubia nam donec aenean eget justo consequat fusce in.
            Varius netus hendrerit dictum dapibus fermentum. Massa eleifend curabitur risus urna cras elementum. Egestas ut lorem proin, cursus convallis aliquam. Nisl augue accumsan facilisi dapibus natoque faucibus tristique. Adipiscing vitae auctor platea etiam suscipit integer primis 
          
          </h1>
          </div>
        </main>
        
        <%  } else { %>

          <form action="/news/choose" method="POST">
            
            <div class="container mb-5 ">
              <div class="form-floating " id="firstContainer" >
                <input class="form-control " id="floatingInput" name="stock" type="text"  >
                <label for="floatingInput" >Search for your desired stock news</label> 
                <div  >
                  <button class="btn btn-dark py-2 btn-lg my-1" type="submit">Search</button>
                </div>
              </div>
            </form>

   <% if(!locals.stock){ %>
        <h1 class="mt-5 mb-5" style="font-family: Verdana, Geneva, Tahoma, sans-serif;" > Latest news related to AAPL</h1>
   <% }else { %>
    <h1 class="mb-5 mt-5" style="font-family: Verdana, Geneva, Tahoma, sans-serif;"> Latest news related to <%=stock%></h1>
    <%} %>
    <div class="row g-5">
    <% for (var i=0; i<title.length;i++){ %>
    <%if(i==title.length-1) {%>
      <div class="col-md-8">
       <%} else { %>
        <div class="col-md-12">
    <%}%>
        <div class="row mb-2">
            <div >
              <div class="row g-0 border rounded overflow-hidden flex-md-row mb-4 shadow-sm h-md-250 position-relative">
                <div class="col p-4 d-flex flex-column position-static">
                  <strong class="d-inline-block mb-2 text-primary-emphasis"><%=publisher[i] %></strong>
                  <h3 class="mb-0"><%=title[i] %></h3>
                  <div class="mb-1 text-body-secondary"><%=time[i] %></div>
                  <img src='<%=image[i]%>' height="250" class="w-50">
                  <p class="card-text mb-auto"><%=content[i] %></p>
                  <strong class="d-inline-block mb-2 text-primary-emphasis"><%=author[i] %></strong>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          </div>
  <%}%>
      <div class="col-md-4">
  
        <div class="position-sticky" style="top: 2rem;">
            <h4 class="fst-italic">Recent news</h4>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
              <li>
                <a class="d-flex flex-column flex-lg-row gap-3 align-items-start align-items-lg-center py-3 link-body-emphasis text-decoration-none border-top" href="<%=url[0]%>">
                  <img class="bd-placeholder-img" width="100%" height="96" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice" focusable="false" src="<%=image[0]%>"><rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="#777"></rect>
                  <div class="col-lg-8">
                    <h5 class="mb-0"><%=title[0]%></h5>
                    <h6 class="mb-0"><%=publisher[0]%></h6>
                    <small class="text-body-secondary"><%=time[0]%></small>
                  </div>
                </a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <a class="d-flex flex-column flex-lg-row gap-3 align-items-start align-items-lg-center py-3 link-body-emphasis text-decoration-none border-top" href="<%=url[1]%>">
                  <img class="bd-placeholder-img" width="100%" height="96" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice" focusable="false" src="<%=image[1]%>"><rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="#777"></rect>
                  <div class="col-lg-8">
                    <h5 class="mb-0"><%=title[1]%></h5>
                    <h6 class="mb-0"><%=publisher[1]%></h6>
                    <small class="text-body-secondary"><%=time[1]%></small>
                  </div>
                </a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <a class="d-flex flex-column flex-lg-row gap-3 align-items-start align-items-lg-center py-3 link-body-emphasis text-decoration-none border-top" href="<%=url[2]%>">
                  <img class="bd-placeholder-img" width="100%" height="96" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice" focusable="false" src="<%=image[2]%>"><rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="#777"></rect>
                  <div class="col-lg-8">
                    <h5 class="mb-0"> <%=title[2]%></h5>
                    <h6 class="mb-0"><%=publisher[2]%></h6>
                    <small class="text-body-secondary"><%=time[2]%></small>
                  </div>
                </a>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  
  </main>
</body>
<% } %>
<%- include("partials/footer.ejs"); %>

</html>


